Package: SIMPLICA
Title: Biclustering via Simplivariate Component Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Jos", "Hageman", email = "jos.hageman@wur.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identifies constant, additive, multiplicative, and user-defined 
    simplivariate components in numeric data matrices using a genetic algorithm. 
    Allows flexible pattern definitions and provides visualization tools for 
    biclustering applications in life sciences and chemometrics.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
Imports:
    GA,
    ggplot2,
    ggsci
URL: https://github.com/joshageman/SIMPLICA
BugReports: https://github.com/joshageman/SIMPLICA/issues
